channel.title: RSPS Project - Need Developers
channel.description:
Starting a new RSPS, last one we created was 2 years ago and was #2 on Mopar for a very long time, over 300 Online on a daily basis.
Hoping to get it started again.
We need:
Web Developers- This includes; PHP, HTML, MySQL, being able to work with HediSQL / IIS Programmers- This includes; Java, VB, being able to work with Dropbox / KVM / Remote access - For connecting to the Dedicated ports. Economic Advisers- This includes; Helping us with the economics part of things, pricing on items, editing them daily, changing stocks and many other things.
Please contact us on Moparscape or on Skype if you're interested.
Skype: Jackhampson
Thanks!
